item.description:
Still looking for something fun and moderately athletic and social to do?  How about a pickup game of Ultimate Frisbee?

 

Run(slowly out of deference to the heat) around while throwing and catching a plastic disc. It's more fun than it sounds and is a great way to meet new people.

 

Event will be cancelled if less than 6 sign up, or if its raining.
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at the Statue at the North End of the park, (closer to Westminster Street)
item.name: The Return of Ultimate Frisbee!!!
